<br>
So, what do I see when I look at The Newbie Zone (SOE's official message board for EQ) this evening?  They have a new PvP server on Test with an even more unique PvP ruleset than the present 4 (<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum4/HTML/054881.html">boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum4/HTML/054881.html</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->).  What's that about population being a major concern in keeping a server open? <br>
<br>
